short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Symbolab: equation search and math solver - solves algebra, trigonometry and calculus problems step by step

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Symbolab Chrome Extension allow you to take a screenshot of math and STEM related problems and get immediate answer with step-by-step explanation. 

By installing this extension, you agree to Symbolabs's Terms of Use (https://www.symbolab.com/public/terms.pdf) and have read our Privacy Policy (https://www.symbolab.com/privacy-policy).
